  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us to guarantee the internet access for kids</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Most of the children and young people who attend the projects offered by Institute Oswaldo Ribeiro de Mendonca has only one mobile device in their houses and this device is used by the entire family for work. For this reason, during the pandemic, these kids and teenagers don&apos;t have access to online classes of their schools and IORM&apos;s projects. The access to online classes is vital to ensure the continuity of the learning process.</narrative>
  </description>
